"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"lgnd\">",
"    Left panel: Normal surface (SE) and foveolar epithelium (FE) and glands (G). Right panel: Higher power view of the glands shows mucous cells (M) and gastrin-secreting endocrine cells (arrows).",
